### Jobs API Tests
### Make sure to update {{baseUrl}}, {{employerToken}}, and {{jobId}} variables

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@employerToken = YOUR_EMPLOYER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@jobId = 1

### Get all jobs (public, with pagination and filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get all jobs with search filter (search in title, description, requirements)
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?search=developer&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get jobs by location
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?location=Kyiv&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get jobs by employment type
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?employmentType=full-time&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get jobs by work mode
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?workMode=remote&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get only active jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?isActive=true&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get jobs by employer ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?employerId=1&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Complex search: Remote full-time developer jobs in Kyiv
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs?search=developer&location=Kyiv&employmentType=full-time&workMode=remote&isActive=true&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get specific job by ID (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/jobs/{{jobId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create new job (employer only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{employerToken}}

{
  "title": "Senior Backend Developer",
  "description": "We are looking for an experienced Backend Developer to join our team. You will work on building scalable microservices and APIs.",
  "requirements": "5+ years of experience with Node.js and TypeScript, experience with NestJS framework, knowledge of PostgreSQL and MongoDB, experience with Docker and Kubernetes",
  "salaryMin": 3000,
  "salaryMax": 5000,
  "salaryCurrency": "USD",
  "location": "Kyiv",
  "employmentType": "full-time",
  "workMode": "remote"
}

###

### Create internship job
POST {{baseUrl}}/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{employerToken}}

{
  "title": "Frontend Developer Internship",
  "description": "Internship position for junior developers. Learn React, TypeScript and modern web development practices.",
  "location": "Lviv",
  "employmentType": "internship",
  "workMode": "hybrid"
}

###

### Update job (employer only, must be job owner or admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/jobs/{{jobId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{employerToken}}

{
  "title": "Senior Backend Developer (Updated)",
  "salaryMin": 3500,
  "salaryMax": 6000
}

###

### Deactivate job (employer only, must be job owner or admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/jobs/{{jobId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{employerToken}}

{
  "isActive": false
}

###

### Delete job (employer only, must be job owner or admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/jobs/{{jobId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{employerToken}}

###
